Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:32.20,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsudzukishi mitaiken kono monogatari wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:38.03,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,shuugawari no kiseki no shinwa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:58.71,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,wazuka nanoka de sekai wa tsukurareta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:06.05,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,onaji hayasa de kugureru mono sae toriko tosa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:11.65,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,eien nanda to shinjiteita mono mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:17.59,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,onaji ai mo yume mo nanokakan gurai ni genkai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:22.98,OP2 - Romaji,,0,0,0,,dakeredo kawaranai yatsura ga iru to iu
